    "title": "Immediate Requirement Medical Officer at Hinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Medical Officer looking for your next big career move? Hinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies in Amritsar offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Hinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies:\nHinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Hinduja Healthcare Digital Technologies!",
